interpretation.rising_ad_line: Indicates broad market participation and healthy uptrend
interpretation.declining_ad_line: Suggests weakening breadth and potential trend exhaustion
interpretation.divergence_bullish: Index declining but A/D line rising = potential reversal up
interpretation.divergence_bearish: Index rising but A/D line declining = potential reversal down

field_descriptions.advances: Number of stocks that closed higher than previous day
field_descriptions.declines: Number of stocks that closed lower than previous day
field_descriptions.ad_line: Cumulative advance-decline line (running total of net_advances)
field_descriptions.statistics: Summary statistics and trend analysis of the A/D line
